public static void main(String[] args) {
    Scanner scanner = new Scanner(System.in);
    System.out.print("Enter your name: ");
    String name = scanner.nextLine();

    // Limit the input length to prevent buffer overflow
    String safeName = name.substring(0, Math.min(name.length(), 10));

    char[] buffer = new char[10];

    // Copying the limited user input into the buffer
    safeName.getChars(0, safeName.length(), buffer, 0);

    System.out.println("Hello, " + new String(buffer));
}

### Explanation:
취약유형: Buffer Overflow
